OL,3,CLate-night social media spat lands
OL,4,Cfootballer in hot water
OL,6,FAn international footballer has been
OL,7,Freprimanded by his club after making
OL,8,Fderogatory comments to a fan in a late-
OL,9,Fnight social media spat.
OL,11,FNorwich City centre-back Shane Duffy,
OL,12,Fwho has more than 60 caps for the
OL,13,FRepublic of Ireland, hit back at a
OL,14,Fsupporter on X following a 1-0 defeat
OL,15,Fto Derby County on Tuesday - a result
OL,16,Fthat pushed the Canaries into the
OL,17,FChampionship relegation zone.
