OL,6,FDuffy, 33, wasn't involved in the
OL,7,Fmatch and hasn't played for the club
OL,8,Fso far this season after falling out
OL,9,Fof favour following the arrival of new
OL,10,Fhead coach Liam Manning.
OL,12,FHe's also currently nursing a calf
OL,13,Finjury.
OL,15,FEx-Brighton defender Duffy has since
OL,16,Fapologised for the outburst in which
OL,17,Fhe called a fan a 'k**b' and a 'gimp',
OL,18,Fwith Manning confirming during a press
OL,19,Fconference ahead of Saturday's match
OL,20,Fat Swansea City that the matter has
OL,21,Fbeen "dealt with internally."
