OL,6,F"In today's world, you can't do it,"
OL,7,FManning said.
OL,9,F"I spoke with him this morning. We
OL,10,Fspoke in my office, he apologised for
OL,11,Fit - but ultimately, you can't do it.
OL,13,F"He cares, but in today's world, you
OL,14,Fcan't respond. We're always going to
OL,15,Fbe in the firing line, so just don't
OL,16,Fget involved in it. Just stay away
OL,17,Ffrom it, keep your opinions to
OL,18,Fyourself."
