OL,6,FPosting on X the morning after the
OL,7,Fmatch, Duffy admitted that his
OL,8,Ffrustration had got the better of him:
OL,9,F"It's been a tough period, and seeing
OL,10,Fthe criticism towards the team has
OL,11,Fbeen hard.
OL,13,F"We have to accept the criticism right
OL,14,Fnow.
OL,16,F"Everyone here cares a lot about
OL,17,Fperforming well, and sometimes
OL,18,Femotions get the better of you when
OL,19,Fthings aren't going as planned."
