OL,6,F"My comment came out of frustration,
OL,7,Fnot a lack of respect for the
OL,8,Fsupporters ` we really do value your
OL,9,Fpassion and backing. I apologise for
OL,10,Fmy comments."
OL,12,FDuffy is currently serving a three-
OL,13,Fyear driving ban after admitting a
OL,14,Fdrink-drive charge following an
OL,15,Fincident in Hethersett, near Norwich,
OL,16,Fin which he hit a stationary car while
OL,17,Fover the limit.
